Round_Rock.Round Rock High School:
Round Rock High School is a 6A high school within the Round Rock Independent School District in Round Rock, Texas. During the late 1990s, it was the largest high school in Central Texas.
As of the 2014-15 school year, the school had an enrollment of 2,972 students and 195.6 classroom teachers (on an FTE basis), for a student–teacher ratio of 15.2:1.
